@startuml
title Registration Flow

actor Student
participant "Web UI" as UI
participant "Next.js API /api/registrations" as API
participant "Prisma / PostgreSQL" as DB

Student -> UI : Click Register
UI -> API : POST /api/registrations { eventId }
API -> DB : validate capacity, create registration, generate qrCode
DB --> API : registration record
API --> UI : 201 Created + registration id
UI --> Student : Show ticket / QR code

@enduml
